    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Hospitalisation in intensive care unit

          -  Acute brain injury (trauma, subarachnoid haemorrhage, stroke, infection) with Glasgow
             Coma Scale &lt;= 12

          -  Age between 18 and 75 years

          -  Mechanical ventilation &gt; 24 hours

        Exclusion Criteria:

